<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.4">
<l>tārāya taṇṭuḷapa vaṇṭuḻuta varaimārpa ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>pōrāṉaik kompocitta puṭpāka ṉeṉṉammā ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>ārāṉuṅ kāṇmiṉka ḷampavaḷam vāyavaṉuk keṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kārvāṉam niṉṟatiruk kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The one with a mountain[-like] chest where bees burrow in the fresh tulasī</l>
<l rend="indent">fit for a garland,” she declares;</l>
<l>“My lord is the one who rides the bird [and who] broke the tusk</l>
<l rend="indent">of the battle elephant,” she declares;</l>
<l>“Everyone look; he has lovely coral lips,” she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram where the clouds,</l>
<l rend="indent">lingering in the skies, thunder?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
